Titolo: Otocadoll

Anno: 2015

Descrizione: Otocadoll (オトカドール, Otoka dōru) is a Japanese arcade game created by Konami. The game consists on magical idols known as a "Dolls" who gather energy through the rhythm of songs, which is used to defeat rivals or monsters. To play it the User is required to have a ticket that will identify them as an idol. It was released on March 13, 2015 and is currently in its 3rd-4th year. Periodically, new songs, outfits, and characters are released.

Genere: Rhythm game

Valutazione: N/A
